{"tid":1752302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（真係要討論）真係用咗陶傑方案","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T02:53:35.000Z","uid":51200,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca765f478871e1bc7db592139f07dec7edecaf5c","tid":1752302,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:43:28.000Z","msg":"陶傑好似一早知道劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八奇思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n１）引用基本法１６條，以援助為由出動解放軍，到道路上清路障<br />\n<br />\n２）解放軍不帶任何裝備、不矇面，只穿背心，清除路面雜物<br />\n<br />\n３）示威者成功引解放軍出動，攬炒目的已達到<br />\n<br />\n４）解放軍出動之後，馬上成立獨立調查委員會，清算濫捕濫暴警察，將違法警察送上法庭，重建法治信心。<br />\n<br />\n５）警察即使被清算，但因解放軍在港，而不敢倒戈／政變<br />\n<br />\n６）成立清算警察機制之後，民情緩和，區選如期舉行，容許泛民大勝。<br />\n<br />\n７）激烈局勢於１２月中平息，宣佈普選具體方案，指令林鄭下台，全體政府高官班底重組。<br />\n<br />\nCLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31aa3471e4b3222a352169e0dca91823c048ef4c","tid":1752302,"uid":165669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:45:51.000Z","msg":"清算警察呢？"},{"pid":"576716355d9b00db8c49fdf9262d7d8de020c14d","tid":1752302,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:07.000Z","msg":"清算？"},{"pid":"9d7e689cc03c325576cec780a4aec0581a15790c","tid":1752302,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:38.000Z","msg":"有咩好討論 <br />\n主流民意就係想要呢d野"},{"pid":"4bbb75458ddde4263e91ad02adbb7b25793f0df3","tid":1752302,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:53.000Z","msg":"清算？"},{"pid":"ea71e2c36f1886fc8bf34c6b07d223f7e60de1f2","tid":1752302,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:48:05.000Z","msg":"先唔講冇清算警察 我深信香港人唔會因為贏咗嗰區選而放棄五大訴求 唔會當手足係condom"},{"pid":"b6e1376a05dc61443c83304d33aeff8390a680e0","tid":1752302,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:48:07.000Z","msg":"成立清算警察機制之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d4f2f8778d5627534e15c51dc969b064dc3807","tid":1752302,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:52:23.000Z","msg":"反而想講因為香港人政治上表達左核爆都唔割嘅思想<br />\n而家71.2% 投票率，<br />\n即係除非另外冇投嘅全部被中共買晒<br />\n如果唔係我方都實超過<br />\n<br />\n但一定要吸引更多人支持我方再壯大實力<br />\n同時因為政治上被香港人突破左<br />\n所以中共將來應該用經濟手段控制香港人<br />\n所以都要睇路"},{"pid":"b76f709934433fea76570cad31b0d8adcbabffa1","tid":1752302,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf0931cec9c45de3ae90af75f833942c20e60a1","tid":1752302,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}